The,CloudSight,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,image,recognition,services,into,their,apps,Its,calls,allow,developers,to,submit,an,image,and,receive,a,description,of,the,image,s,contents,in,return,CloudSight,works,even,when,the,end,user,takes,a,picture,at,the,wrong,angle,or,in,poor,lighting,conditions,CloudSight,recognizes,nearly,million,images